g.text: This workflow focuses on the variables we can extract from energy consumption data.
For more information see the workflow metadata. Find it here: View -> Description
The energy used is calculated for each meter ID in average and as percentage
(Monday, Tuesday, etc ... and business days vs. week ends)
Here we calculate the auto-correlation matrix for a single selected
meter ID. Auto-correlation is calculated on 100 past samples.
This number can be changed in the "Normalize & Lag" metanode.
